 - Fractions constant rewrite rules.

 - >>> (sin x) ^ 2 + (cos x) ^ 2
   sin(x) ^ 2 + cos(x) ^ 2
   >>> sin(x) ^ 2 + cos(x) ^ 2
   sin(x ^ 2) + cos(x ^ 2)

